PROGRAMME 5

Map with Hotspots + Frames
File 1: map_index.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<frameset cols="30%,70%">
    <frame src="links.html">
    <frame src="map.html" name="content">
</frameset>
</html>
File 2: links.html
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<body>

<h3>Campus Areas</h3>

